    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If I understand correctly the issue was: the settings were not applied on the replicas right? Yes it's the expected behaviour. You have to provide an options to apply the [`setSettings`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-methods/set-settings/?language=javascript) call to the replicas, it's [`forwardToReplicas `](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-methods/set-settings/?language=javascript#method-param-forwardtoreplicas).",
